Dialogue: 50,0:00:53.04,0:00:55.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,How long are you gonna keep moping?
Dialogue: 50,0:00:58.10,0:01:02.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{All the treasure we hid \Nin the Middle Forest is gone. -OG}All the treasure we hid \Nin the midway forest is gone.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:01:02.57,0:01:06.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,But that pile of loot doesn't matter anymore.
Dialogue: 50,0:01:06.41,0:01:11.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sabo and I were gonna use it.\NIt was our pirate fund.
Dialogue: 50,0:01:11.73,0:01:15.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,But in the end, Sabo didn't use it.
Dialogue: 50,0:01:15.30,0:01:19.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And so, I'm not gonna bother with it either. -OG}And so, I won't worry about it either.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:01:19.38,0:01:23.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There's no point in gathering treasure if we can't even look after it. -OG}There's no point in gathering\Ntreasure you can't even protect.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:01:23.29,0:01:25.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A-Ace...
Dialogue: 50,0:01:25.45,0:01:26.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 50,0:01:29.14,0:01:31.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I want to become stronger! -OG}I wanna get stronger!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:01:32.51,0:01:33.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stronger and stronger! -OG}And stronger...{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:01:33.76,0:01:35.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stronger...! -OG}and stronger...!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:01:35.28,0:01:37.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Stronger and stronger!
Dialogue: 50,0:01:37.31,0:01:38.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stronger and stronger! -OG}Lots stronger!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:01:38.99,0:01:40.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Stronger!
Dialogue: 50,0:01:40.13,0:01:42.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stronger and stronger! -OG}Lots and lots stronger!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:01:42.08,0:01:43.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Stronger and stronger!
Dialogue: 50,0:01:43.88,0:01:45.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stronger and stronger! Stronger and stronger! -OG}So much stronger!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:01:45.66,0:01:47.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stronger and stronger! Stronger and stronger! -OG}And stronger and stronger!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:01:47.62,0:01:50.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,And even stronger than that!
Dialogue: 50,0:01:50.02,0:01:53.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,And then, I'll be able to protect anything.
Dialogue: 50,0:01:53.39,0:01:55.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I won't have to lose anyone ever again!
Dialogue: 50,0:01:57.27,0:01:59.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Please... -OG}So please...{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:01:59.74,0:02:04.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ace... don't die!
Dialogue: 50,0:02:04.08,0:02:06.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 50,0:02:06.11,0:02:08.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You should be more worried\Nabout yourself than me! -OG}You should worry more \Nabout yourself, not me!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:02:08.89,0:02:10.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're way weaker than I am! -OG}You're way weaker than me!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:02:11.26,0:02:14.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Listen up, and remember this, Luffy!
Dialogue: 50,0:02:14.87,0:02:16.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I will not die! -OG}I'm not gonna die!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:02:21.38,0:02:24.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sabo made that request, too.{Z- I think this refers to when Ace says "Sabo told me to take care of you!"}
Dialogue: 50,0:02:24.86,0:02:28.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I promise. I will not die! -OG}I promise. I won't die!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:02:29.21,0:02:32.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There's no way I'd die \Nand leave behind a weakling of a brother like you! -OG}I won't leave my crybaby brother behind!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:02:35.57,0:02:42.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm not all that smart, so I don't know \Nwhat even killed Sabo. -OG}I'm not very clever, so I don't know \Nwho—or even what—killed Sabo.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:02:42.36,0:02:46.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But whatever it was, it was definitely the opposite of freedom! -OG}But whatever happened,\Nit was definitely the opposite of freedom!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:02:46.90,0:02:50.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Sabo died without ever gaining his freedom... -OG}Sabo died before he could truly be free.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:02:50.61,0:02:54.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,But the two of us, who shared\Na toast with Sabo, are still alive!{Z- Hard to get this line to sound natural. Viz has this as "But Sabo was our brother. And we're still alive!"}
Dialogue: 50,0:02:57.96,0:03:00.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,So, listen up, Luffy.
Dialogue: 50,0:03:00.87,0:03:05.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We have to live our lives without regrets! -OG}We have to live our lives... with no regrets!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:03:20.24,0:03:22.54,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Noblemen only become true nobles -OG}In this kingdom...{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:03:22.54,0:03:26.15,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{once they turn eighteen. -OG}we become true nobles on our 18th birthday.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:03:27.19,0:03:31.22,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's why I will leave this kingdom when I turn seventeen! -OG}So before that,\NI'll leave this country at 17!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:03:33.88,0:03:38.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Someday, we'll head out to sea,
Dialogue: 50,0:03:39.13,0:03:41.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and then we'll be able to do whatever we want! -OG}so we can live however we want!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:03:41.38,0:03:43.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No one will have more freedom than us! -OG}We'll be more free than anyone!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:03:46.14,0:03:51.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm sure that will make \Nlots of people into our enemies... -OG}I'm sure we'll make lots\Nof enemies because of that.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:03:51.05,0:03:55.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Gramps will become our enemy, too.\NWe'll be risking our lives. -OG}Even Grandpa will fight us.\NWe'll be risking our lives.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:03:55.91,0:03:58.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We'll cast off when we turn seventeen! -OG}We set sail at 17!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:03:58.39,0:04:00.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We will become pirates! -OG}And then...{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:04:00.19,0:04:01.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We will become pirates! -OG}we will become pirates!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:06:58.00,0:07:00.58,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,Again, we turn back time a little...
Dialogue: 50,0:07:00.58,0:07:04.50,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,to the night when the Celestial Dragon's\Nship docked in Goa Kingdom.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:05.81,0:07:12.10,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{In a small village in a certain region of East Blue... -OG}In a certain region of the East Blue,\Nin a small seaside village...{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:07:22.65,0:07:26.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Did you see that guy with the huge face\Nwho was here this afternoon? -OG}Did you see the guy\Nwith the huge face this afternoon?!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:07:26.09,0:07:28.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I've never seen anything like it!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:28.09,0:07:31.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Look! His ship is huge too!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:31.39,0:07:33.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Five hundred and eighty...
Dialogue: 50,0:07:33.83,0:07:35.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Five hundred and eighty-one...
Dialogue: 50,0:07:35.83,0:07:38.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Five hundred and eighty-two...
Dialogue: 50,0:07:38.60,0:07:40.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Five hundred and eighty-three...
Dialogue: 50,0:07:40.94,0:07:42.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Five hundred and eighty-four...
Dialogue: 50,0:07:46.75,0:07:49.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Vyou're late, Dragon! -OG}You are late, Dragon!{Z- oof, that 1-for-1 accent translation (shudder)}
Dialogue: 50,0:07:49.00,0:07:52.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How long did vyou plan to keep vus waiting?! -OG}How long did you plan to make us vayyt?!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:07:53.92,0:07:54.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 50,0:07:55.79,0:07:57.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Vyou... What's that? -OG}Vhaat did you...?!{Z- I wanted to make this line a bit more ambiguous for those viewers who aren't in the know about Sabo's fate yet.}
Dialogue: 50,0:07:58.00,0:07:59.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,This is awful!
Dialogue: 50,0:07:59.25,0:08:01.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You! Quickly, bring a doctor!\NThis is an emergency! -OG}Quickly! Get a doctor! It's an emergency!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:08:01.40,0:08:02.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Right away!
Dialogue: 50,0:08:05.00,0:08:09.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Really... Where have vyou been?! -OG}But really! Vherre did you go?!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:08:09.46,0:08:12.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I was watching the ceremony\Nfor the world nobles.
Dialogue: 50,0:08:14.66,0:08:18.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How could vyou go there on vyour own,\Nwithout telling vme about it! -OG}How could you go attend\Non your own viithout tellingk me?!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:08:19.34,0:08:22.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you'd been there, we'd have stood out too much. -OG}With you there too, we would've\Nstuck out like sore thumbs.{Z- the tact of the Monkey family...}
Dialogue: 50,0:08:24.47,0:08:25.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This... -OG}You mean... thiss...?!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:08:28.05,0:08:32.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We must grow stronger as quickly as possible. -OG}We must strive to grow\Never stronger, and with haste!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:08:33.44,0:08:34.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,How are our provisions?
Dialogue: 50,0:08:35.39,0:08:37.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{A dojo in the village offered us some food. -OG}There was a village dojo\Nthat offered us food.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:08:41.55,0:08:43.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Time to set sail! -OG}Then we set sail!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:08:43.26,0:08:45.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We're going back to Baltigo! -OG}We will return to Baltigo.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:08:51.74,0:08:53.48,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,Some months later,
Dialogue: 50,0:08:53.48,0:08:57.48,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{after the World Government's inspection of Goa Kingdom... -OG}the World Government having concluded\Ntheir inspection of the Kingdom of Goa...{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:09:01.87,0:09:04.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,They've brought more trash!
Dialogue: 50,0:09:05.59,0:09:09.43,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{The people have settled into their old routines... -OG}The people are returning to their old ways,{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:09:10.37,0:09:14.40,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{The trash mountain is back, just like it was before. -OG}and the Gray Terminal is back,\Njust like it was before.{Z- DemonRin, please check to make sure this is "the Gray Terminal" and shouldn't be "trash mountain."}
Dialogue: 50,0:09:18.76,0:09:22.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Here I come, Ace!
Dialogue: 50,0:09:22.68,0:09:24.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 50,0:09:25.34,0:09:27.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Pistol!
Dialogue: 50,0:09:41.24,0:09:43.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What the hell was that?\NYou call this a fight?
Dialogue: 50,0:09:46.83,0:09:51.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No matter how much force you put into it,\Nthere's no point if you can't hit me. -OG}You might pack a punch,\Nbut what's the use if you miss every time?{Z- DemonRin, another non-canon line that needs checking.}
Dialogue: 50,0:09:51.00,0:09:54.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I told you, rubber really isn't suited for battle.
Dialogue: 50,0:09:54.20,0:09:55.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Don't say that!
Dialogue: 50,0:09:56.16,0:09:59.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What?! Are you trying to say that I'm wrong?! -OG}Okay, {\i1}what{\i0}?!\NWanna prove me wrong?!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:09:59.02,0:10:02.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You're just an anchor\Nwho's immune to bulletfire!{Z- DemonRin, Viz has "You gave up your ability to swim and all you got was immunity to blunt force attacks!" I think I prefer the anime translation here.}
Dialogue: 50,0:10:02.82,0:10:06.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't make fun of the Rubber Fruit!\NSomeday, I'll make you cry! -OG}The Gum-Gum Fruit is awesome!\NSomeday, I'll prove you wrong!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:10:06.80,0:10:09.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{After all, I've thought up a technique more powerful than a pistol! -OG}Soon, my pistol isn't\Ngonna be my only move!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:10:10.32,0:10:12.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy, great work!
Dialogue: 50,0:10:12.77,0:10:16.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Your arm stretched a lot further\Nthan it did yesterday!
Dialogue: 50,0:10:16.76,0:10:19.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Sabo! You're far too soft on Luffy! -OG}Sabo! You're too soft on Luffy!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:10:19.84,0:10:23.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I really have become strong!\NStronger than I was yesterday! -OG}I {\i1}knew{\i0} I was getting stronger!\NEven more than yesterday!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:10:23.13,0:10:25.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, Sabo! -OG}Right, Sabo?!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:10:42.17,0:10:45.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Sabo was such a kind older brother... -OG}Sabo was a nicer older brother.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:10:45.08,0:10:47.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What's that supposed to mean?!\NWould you rather I died instead?! -OG}Say {\i1}what{\i0}?!\NYou wish I'd died instead?!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:10:56.02,0:10:57.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ow. -OG}Huh?{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:11:07.83,0:11:09.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I've founded my own country.
Dialogue: 50,0:11:10.39,0:11:12.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A country?
Dialogue: 50,0:11:14.00,0:11:15.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What's this? -OG}Another?{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:11:17.68,0:11:18.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 50,0:11:25.15,0:11:27.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What is it now? -OG}Is this really what we're doin' now?!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:11:27.76,0:11:32.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna learn to survive on my own.\NYou guys can be Dadan's country.
Dialogue: 50,0:11:32.97,0:11:34.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna borrow your bath every now and then. -OG}I'll borrow the bath sometimes.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:11:59.70,0:12:02.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ace! Help me out! It's a bear!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:03.90,0:12:06.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You're gonna survive on your own, right?
Dialogue: 50,0:12:09.01,0:12:10.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:20.36,0:12:21.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:33.73,0:12:36.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Dadan's country, is anyone here?! -OG}Hey! Dadan's country! Anyone there?!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:12:36.12,0:12:39.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Luffy is injured!\NPlease, treat his wounds! -OG}Luffy got hurt! He needs first aid!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:12:41.01,0:12:43.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Magra! Please, help Luffy!
Dialogue: 50,0:12:43.92,0:12:46.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now, now... take it easy! \NCome in, quickly! -OG}Now, take it easy!\NHurry! Bring him in!{Z}
