Dialogue: 50,0:13:02.72,0:13:07.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,If his wounds had been any worse,\Nhe could have died!
Dialogue: 50,0:13:09.32,0:13:12.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The three of you always fought these wild beasts together as a team, right? -OG}You used to take on these\Nwild beasts as a trio, right?{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:13:14.76,0:13:16.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,It's my fault!
Dialogue: 50,0:13:17.40,0:13:21.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I thought that I learned that fighting on your own -OG}I should've already learned my lesson that fighting on your own{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:13:21.45,0:13:23.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,doesn't prove that you're strong!
Dialogue: 50,0:13:24.60,0:13:27.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'm worthless!
Dialogue: 50,0:13:27.09,0:13:29.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Completely worthless!
Dialogue: 50,0:13:32.77,0:13:34.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ace...
Dialogue: 50,0:13:34.19,0:13:36.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Luffy!
Dialogue: 50,0:13:37.82,0:13:38.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,So sorry!
Dialogue: 50,0:13:48.61,0:13:50.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 50,0:13:50.98,0:13:54.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Makino-{\i1}chan{\i0} came all the way\Nout here to bring us some drinks!
Dialogue: 50,0:13:55.43,0:13:58.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,How to greet people properly?{Z- DemonRin, Viz has something different, "You want to know how to thank someone?"}
Dialogue: 50,0:13:58.77,0:14:00.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 50,0:14:00.10,0:14:02.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What brought about this change of attitude? -OG}Why the sudden interest in manners?{Z- probably not 1-for-1 translation, but the English needs to pinpoint Makino's meaning a bit more, IMO}
Dialogue: 50,0:14:02.12,0:14:04.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm Luffy's brother, after all. -OG}Well, it's 'cause I'm Luffy's big brother.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:14:04.66,0:14:11.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Someday, I'd like to meet Captain Red Hair, and\Nthank him for everything he did for my little brother. -OG}I'd like to formally meet this Captain Red Hair\Nand thank him for everything he did for Luffy.{Z- DemonRin, I have two versions here for you: the first is what's displayed on screen, as it plays off of the current translation "How to greet people properly." If we go with Viz's version though, this should say: "I plan to someday meet this Captain Red Hair and properly thank him for everything he did for Luffy." Oh, and Viz points out that Shanks saved Luffy, so I'm not sure if we need to also make that distinction here.}
Dialogue: 50,0:14:20.58,0:14:22.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why're you looking at me like that?! -OG}What's that look for?!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:14:23.72,0:14:25.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 50,0:14:25.54,0:14:28.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But alright, I'll tell you. -OG}Okay then, here's what you say.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:14:28.14,0:14:30.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,So, first of all...
Dialogue: 50,0:14:30.55,0:14:32.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,They ate and ran!
Dialogue: 50,0:14:32.75,0:14:34.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 50,0:14:36.98,0:14:41.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh, we're being rude here!
Dialogue: 50,0:14:41.10,0:14:41.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 50,0:14:46.06,0:14:48.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 50,0:14:48.47,0:14:51.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you damn kids!\NJust pay the bill!
Dialogue: 50,0:14:54.44,0:14:56.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna win today!
Dialogue: 50,0:15:32.09,0:15:33.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Alright! -OG}Yes!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:15:33.72,0:15:35.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Today, we'll be having bear stew for dinner! -OG}Tonight, we're having bear stew!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:17:04.19,0:17:06.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Take care, Ace!
Dialogue: 50,0:17:06.20,0:17:10.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sure! See you later, Luffy!\NI'll be going on ahead!
Dialogue: 50,0:17:10.14,0:17:15.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Right! And when I set out to sea myself in three years, I'll be much stronger! -OG}Yeah! And in three years\Nwhen I set out, I'll be much stronger!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:17:21.99,0:17:25.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Do your best, Ace! -OG}Give it your all, Ace!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:17:25.13,0:17:26.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Take care of yourself!
Dialogue: 50,0:17:26.88,0:17:28.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Try not to catch a cold!
Dialogue: 50,0:17:28.79,0:17:32.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Just you wait! I'll make\Na name for myself real soon!
Dialogue: 50,0:17:34.09,0:17:38.39,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ace, the son of the Pirate King\Nwho had grown up in secret... -OG}Ace, the son of the Pirate King,\Ngrew up in complete secrecy.{Z- Pirate King capitalized here since this is Roger's epithet, and it's only lowercase when by itself as a title that's passed down after Roger's death... I know, super confusing. There was a whole nerd discussion about it.}
Dialogue: 50,0:17:38.39,0:17:43.01,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{quietly set sail from the coast at the foot of Mt. Colubo. -OG}His departure from the coast of Mount Colubo\Nwas kept modest as well.{Z- or something to this effect... Like, Ace's formative years were a secret, and his departure was likewise kept quiet. I dunno.}
Dialogue: 50,0:17:59.30,0:18:01.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,There he goes.{Z- DemonRin, Viz says "He's still waving!"}
Dialogue: 50,0:18:01.91,0:18:05.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Really, how is Garp going to take this? -OG}Isn't anyone worried\Nabout how Garp will take this?{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:18:23.78,0:18:25.96,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{You raise him, Dadan. -OG}You're gonna raise him, Dadan!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:18:25.96,0:18:29.29,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(2081,2830,1,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}{You gotta be kidding me! Whose kid is that?! -OG}No, wait! Whose kid is that?!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:18:29.92,0:18:32.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Boss...
Dialogue: 50,0:18:32.20,0:18:34.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ace has just left. -OG}Ace just left.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:18:35.71,0:18:41.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That so? I'm the one who'll get scolded by Garp for this... -OG}Did he, now? I'd better brace\Nmyself to get scolded by Garp.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:18:41.46,0:18:43.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That little brat was just hopeless. -OG}That brat was nothin' but hopeless.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:18:43.91,0:18:48.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, right, I have a message to you from Ace. -OG}Oh, and Ace left a message for you!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:18:48.01,0:18:53.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What?! Even now, after he's left, he's still complaining to me?! -OG}What?! He's gone, but he wants\Nto complain one last time?!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:18:53.10,0:18:55.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,He said, "Sorry for all the trouble, and thanks."
Dialogue: 50,0:19:01.22,0:19:04.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That idiot, he can't be serious! -OG}Why'd that moron have to go and say that?!{Z}
