Dialogue: 50,0:19:08.54,0:19:10.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'm not crying, you idiot!
Dialogue: 50,0:19:23.27,0:19:25.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Only three more years for me!
