Dialogue: 50,0:19:28.14,0:19:29.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Pistol!
Dialogue: 50,0:19:32.79,0:19:36.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Damn... My aim was off. -OG}Damn! Just a little off.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:19:37.90,0:19:42.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That was close, Luffy.\NWhy don't you just aim a little lower? -OG}That was close, Luffy!\NTry aiming just a little lower.{Z}
