Dialogue: 50,0:19:48.80,0:19:49.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Pistol!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:03.65,0:20:05.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll become stronger! -OG}I'm getting stronger!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:20:05.75,0:20:09.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(2590,3410,1,\c&H000000&)}Much stronger!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:16.88,0:20:18.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:18.40,0:20:20.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Look at the newspapers! -OG}Check out the newspaper!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:20:20.33,0:20:21.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What is it? -OG}What's up?{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:20:21.75,0:20:23.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Look at this! -OG}Look! Look!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:20:23.74,0:20:26.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Amazing! Ace made a name for himself! -OG}So cool! Ace is famous now!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:20:26.70,0:20:29.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The picture shows him with his pirate ship and crew! -OG}It's a picture of his pirate ship and crew!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:20:29.09,0:20:33.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Amazing! Ace is amazing!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:34.45,0:20:36.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm not gonna lose to him! -OG}I gotta catch up to him!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:20:44.72,0:20:46.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:46.59,0:20:49.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm going now. Aren't you gonna see me off? -OG}I'm leaving. You gonna see me off?{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:20:49.54,0:20:51.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 50,0:20:51.10,0:20:52.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, shut up... -OG}Shut up!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:20:53.12,0:20:55.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The mayor and Makino know us, -OG}The mayor and Makino might know us,{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:20:55.37,0:21:00.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but we'd scare the other villagers if we came down from the mountain. -OG}but we'd send the rest of Foosha Village\Ninto a panic if we came down the mountain!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:21:00.24,0:21:01.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 50,0:21:01.96,0:21:03.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Just get going already!
Dialogue: 50,0:21:04.42,0:21:07.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh... okay. Well then, guys! -OG}Oh, okay. Well then, guys,{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:21:07.52,0:21:09.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Thanks for everything! -OG}thanks for everything!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:21:09.78,0:21:12.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't embarrass us.\NNo need for thanks.
Dialogue: 50,0:21:12.90,0:21:15.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now, now... Take care. -OG}Now, take it easy.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:21:15.46,0:21:17.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Sure, I will! -OG}Yep! Sure thing!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:21:19.22,0:21:20.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 50,0:21:21.25,0:21:24.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dadan! I hate mountain bandits!
Dialogue: 50,0:21:24.27,0:21:25.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Shut up, you little brat! -OG}Shut up, you little turd!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:21:27.05,0:21:29.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{...but I like you guys! -OG}But I like you guys!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:21:33.14,0:21:36.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't say dumb stuff like that,\Nand just get lost, damn you! -OG}Don't say dumb stuff like that!\NJust get lost, dammit!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:21:36.91,0:21:41.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Sheesh, you guys are just... -OG}You're really just all the same!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:21:42.13,0:21:43.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What, are you crying?
Dialogue: 50,0:21:43.84,0:21:46.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No, I'm not! -OG}No! I'm absolutely not!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:21:47.95,0:21:52.45,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Windmill Village, at the outskirts of the Goa Kingdom on Dawn Island... -OG}Foosha Village, at the outskirts of the\NKingdom of Goa on Dawn Island...{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:21:52.89,0:21:56.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, if you're going out to sea,\Nthen you should take my old fishing boat, Luffy! -OG}Hey! You're going out to sea, so just\Ntake my old fishing boat, Luffy!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:21:56.89,0:21:59.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You'll sink right away if you take that thing! -OG}You'll sink right away in that thing!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:21:59.43,0:22:01.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{A rowing boat? Come on, now! -OG}A rowboat? C'mon!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:22:02.28,0:22:05.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm fine with this. My journey begins right now! -OG}It's gotta be this way!\NThis is where everything begins for me!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:22:09.81,0:22:12.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sabo!
Dialogue: 50,0:22:12.71,0:22:18.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Look at me!\NI'm setting out to sea too!
Dialogue: 50,0:22:20.11,0:22:23.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sabo was first. Ace was second.
Dialogue: 50,0:22:24.28,0:22:27.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm the third to go,\Nbut I won't lose! -OG}I'm the third to go,\Nbut I won't lose to them!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:22:27.23,0:22:31.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wait for me, Ace!\NI'll catch up to you soon! -OG}Wait for me, Ace!\NSoon, I'm gonna catch up!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:22:31.46,0:22:34.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What are you doing, Luffy?\NShouting and muttering to yourself like that...? -OG}What's all this, Luffy?\NShouting to yourself like that?{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:22:34.48,0:22:36.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Is it some sort of good luck charm?
Dialogue: 50,0:22:36.64,0:22:38.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's not it. It's a challenge! -OG}It's not a charm. It's a challenge!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:22:39.14,0:22:41.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Who's Ace?
Dialogue: 50,0:22:41.02,0:22:41.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No idea. -OG}Not a clue.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:22:41.77,0:22:44.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Alright, I'm going now. -OG}Alright, I'm outta here!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:22:53.31,0:22:56.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There he goes, mayor... -OG}Well, Mayor, he's finally off.{Z}{Same dialogue as Romance Dawn 1 time stamp 17:11}
Dialogue: 50,0:22:56.35,0:22:58.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna miss him.
Dialogue: 50,0:22:58.26,0:23:01.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's a disgrace to the village! Becoming a pirate... -OG}He's disgracing our village\Nby becoming a pirate!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:23:04.13,0:23:09.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ah... It's a great day to set sail! -OG}What a nice day to set sail!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:23:21.64,0:23:22.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 50,0:23:27.14,0:23:29.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So there you are, lord of the coastal waters. -OG}If it isn't our local sea monster.{Z- matches Romance Dawn 01 dialogue}
Dialogue: 50,0:23:34.96,0:23:37.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You picked the wrong opponent. -OG}You don't know who you're messing with.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:23:37.73,0:23:40.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Check out my attack, I've been practicing for the past ten years! -OG}Here's a technique 10 years in the making!{Z}
