Dialogue: 50,0:23:50.11,0:23:52.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Pistol!
Dialogue: 50,0:24:08.89,0:24:10.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Learned your lesson yet, damn fish? -OG}That'll teach ya, damn fish!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:24:18.59,0:24:22.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Incredible... He beat the lord of the coastal waters with one punch! -OG}Incredible! He beat the\NLord of the Coast with one punch!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:24:23.94,0:24:26.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's grown strong. -OG}He's sure grown strong.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:24:28.19,0:24:30.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,First, I've gotta gather a crew.
Dialogue: 50,0:24:30.28,0:24:32.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'd like to have about ten people... -OG}Ten people oughta do it!{Z}
