Dialogue: 50,0:24:36.96,0:24:41.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Alright... Here I come! -OG}Alright! Let's go!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:24:41.96,0:24:43.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be...
Dialogue: 50,0:24:45.66,0:24:48.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{the Pirate King! -OG}king of the pirates!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:24:58.22,0:24:59.88,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{And now we return to the present day... -OG}We return to the present.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:25:01.79,0:25:04.84,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,His brother Ace is dead, and Luffy...
Dialogue: 50,0:25:05.62,0:25:07.26,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{is crying. -OG}sheds his tears.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:25:20.81,0:25:22.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 50,0:25:22.67,0:25:25.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Pirate King? Yeah, right! -OG}Me? The pirate king?{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:25:25.90,0:25:27.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 50,0:25:28.44,0:25:31.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,so weak!
Dialogue: 50,0:25:31.21,0:25:32.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,It's Garp-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 50,0:25:32.48,0:25:34.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Garp-san has returned in a battleship! -OG}Garp-{\i1}san{\i0}'s returned on his battleship!
Dialogue: 50,0:25:34.82,0:25:35.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Is he on official business? -OG}On official business?!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:25:36.22,0:25:39.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Garp-san! I read the article about the war! -OG}Garp-{\i1}san{\i0}! We read all about the war!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:25:39.04,0:25:41.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I heard it was an overwhelming victory for the Navy? -OG}The Navy had a resounding victory, right?!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:25:41.03,0:25:43.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, and I'm glad to see you're all safe. -OG}Yeah, and I'm glad to see you're all well.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:25:43.28,0:25:44.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How is Luffy doing? -OG}Is Luffy okay?!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:25:44.82,0:25:48.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What will happen to the world now that Whitebeard is dead? -OG}With Whitebeard dead,\Nwhat'll happen to the world?!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:25:48.30,0:25:49.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, Garp-san! -OG}Tell us, Garp-{\i1}san{\i0}!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:25:49.40,0:25:54.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,These past few days, we've seen\Na lot of pirate ships on the open sea.
Dialogue: 50,0:25:54.50,0:25:58.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They could attack us anytime,\Nit's keeping us awake at night! -OG}The thought of getting raided\Nkeeps us awake at night!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:25:58.77,0:26:03.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't worry.\NI just sank three of them on the way here. -OG}Rest easy!\NI just sank three of 'em on the way here.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:26:03.97,0:26:06.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Really? What a relief! -OG}Really? That's good to hear!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:26:06.29,0:26:10.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They were just a bunch of amateur pirates\Nwho hadn't even learned how to spell "Battle". -OG}Buncha amateurs like them\Ncan't even spell the word "battle"!{Z- Viz has "They were a bunch of amateurs who had no idea what it means to fight..."}
Dialogue: 50,0:26:10.75,0:26:13.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But still, Whitebeard was a deterrent. -OG}Although, Whitebeard {\i1}was{\i0} a stabilizing factor...{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:26:13.45,0:26:18.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now that the world has lost him, the seas are going to be uneasy for a while. -OG}With him gone, every sea in the world \Nwill be a turbulent place for some time.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:26:18.39,0:26:23.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down just because\Nyou live in a remote part of the East Blue.
Dialogue: 50,0:26:23.02,0:26:23.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Men. -OG}Hey.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:26:23.66,0:26:24.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 50,0:26:25.76,0:26:29.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{"Security - Navy HQ Vice-Admiral Garp," huh? -OG}"Protected Area – Vice Admiral Garp, Navy Headquarters," huh?{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:26:29.01,0:26:30.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,That's so reassuring!
Dialogue: 50,0:26:30.83,0:26:33.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to be afraid of now!
Dialogue: 50,0:26:33.74,0:26:36.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Garp-{\i1}san{\i0}, we have another problem.
Dialogue: 50,0:26:36.74,0:26:41.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bandits came down out of the\Nmountains and took over Makino's bar!
Dialogue: 50,0:26:41.95,0:26:43.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bandits?
Dialogue: 50,0:26:43.15,0:26:45.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Stop! Don't!
Dialogue: 50,0:26:49.90,0:26:51.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey, Garp!
Dialogue: 50,0:26:51.20,0:26:52.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's her!
Dialogue: 50,0:26:54.69,0:26:58.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You've got some nerve\Nshowing your face here again!
Dialogue: 50,0:26:59.29,0:27:01.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Garp-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 50,0:27:01.14,0:27:02.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 50,0:27:02.39,0:27:03.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vice Admiral Garp!
Dialogue: 50,0:27:10.55,0:27:13.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't interfere!\NI know this woman. -OG}Stand down!\NShe and I go way back.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:27:16.17,0:27:17.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 50,0:27:18.62,0:27:21.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You were right there on the battlefield!
Dialogue: 50,0:27:22.23,0:27:24.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They were right there in front of you...  -OG}They were right in front of you!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:27:24.14,0:27:26.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,So, what the hell were you doing?!
Dialogue: 50,0:27:26.32,0:27:28.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What the hell were you doing?!
Dialogue: 50,0:27:28.30,0:27:30.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Why?! Why?! Why?!
Dialogue: 50,0:27:30.84,0:27:33.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why?! Why, dammit?! -OG}Why?! {\i1}Why{\i0}?!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:27:41.01,0:27:44.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why did you just let Ace die like that?! -OG}Why did you just stand there and let Ace die?!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:27:45.15,0:27:48.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Is duty more important than your family?! -OG}Your job {\i1}always{\i0} came before your family!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:27:48.48,0:27:51.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Huh, Garp?!\NWhat kind of hero of the Navy are you?! -OG}Right, Garp?! \NAnd they call you the Hero of the Navy!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:27:51.94,0:27:53.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Just die, you damn old man! -OG}Shrivel up and die, you geezer!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:27:53.83,0:27:56.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now, now, take it easy, boss!\NPlease stop! -OG}Now, take it easy, boss!\NThat's too far!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:27:56.20,0:27:57.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Boss...
Dialogue: 50,0:27:57.09,0:28:00.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Garp, say something!\NWhy didn't you help him?!}Garp, cat got your tongue?!\NYou could have saved him!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:28:00.52,0:28:02.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why didn't you prevent it?! -OG}Why'd you let it happen?!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:28:02.59,0:28:05.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Stand up! Get on your feet!
Dialogue: 50,0:28:05.03,0:28:08.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You inhuman filth!{Z- I love how harsh this is. Not sure if we can up the ante on how mad Dadan is at Garp right now.}
Dialogue: 50,0:28:09.27,0:28:11.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stop it, Dadan-san! -OG}That's enough, Dadan-{\i1}san{\i0}!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:28:17.38,0:28:18.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Makino...
Dialogue: 50,0:28:36.86,0:28:41.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They were within an arm's reach,\Nyet he was unable to help them... -OG}They may have been within arm's reach,\Nbut there was nothing he could do!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:28:41.40,0:28:43.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Garp-san is suffering the most because of this! -OG}The one hurting most here is Garp-{\i1}san{\i0}!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:28:54.16,0:28:55.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Y-You're wrong...
Dialogue: 50,0:28:58.02,0:28:59.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You're wrong...
Dialogue: 50,0:29:00.82,0:29:02.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 50,0:29:03.56,0:29:07.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The one who's in the most pain... is Luffy! -OG}The one who's hurting most... is Luffy!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:29:17.24,0:29:21.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Now, try to imagine that he's\Nright here in front of you.
Dialogue: 50,0:29:21.88,0:29:25.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'm Ace! Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 50,0:29:25.19,0:29:29.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Bzzzz. That's no good. "Who the hell" is too rude. -OG}That's a no-go.\N"Who the hell" is too rude.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:29:29.77,0:29:32.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's "Who're you?!", right? -OG}Is it, "Oh, it's you?!"{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:29:33.01,0:29:34.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Who might you be?
Dialogue: 50,0:29:35.99,0:29:37.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who is this? -OG}And just who are you?{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:29:39.85,0:29:41.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's "Who is that?", right? -OG}Is it, "Who's that?"{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:29:44.37,0:29:47.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,All wrong. Are you even trying?
Dialogue: 50,0:29:47.55,0:29:50.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is all because you keep talking nonsense! -OG}It's your fault for buzzing\Naround with nonsense!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:29:50.44,0:29:51.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Quit distracting me! -OG}Quit it!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:29:51.72,0:29:53.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ace!
Dialogue: 50,0:29:53.07,0:29:58.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yesterday, I found the nest of a giant snake, filled with huge eggs! -OG}Yesterday, I found the nest of a giant snake, \Nand it was filled with humongous eggs!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:29:58.43,0:30:00.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's go get them now! -OG}Let's go get them!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:30:00.08,0:30:02.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Huh? Huge eggs? -OG}Huh? Humongous eggs?{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:30:02.34,0:30:04.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No, I can't right now! -OG}No, not right now!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:30:04.49,0:30:07.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'm studying how to greet people!
Dialogue: 50,0:30:07.28,0:30:11.18,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll be in trouble if that huge snake catches me by myself! -OG}It'll be real bad if that giant snake\Ncatches me when I go by myself!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:30:11.18,0:30:14.54,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{But I'll be fine if you're with me. So come on! -OG}But I'll be fine if you're with me. C'mon!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:30:14.54,0:30:15.76,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 50,0:30:18.34,0:30:22.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Do you have any idea how highly he thought of his brother?! -OG}You have to know how much\Nhe looked up to his brother!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:30:32.00,0:30:32.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Makino!
Dialogue: 50,0:30:35.80,0:30:37.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Garp...
Dialogue: 50,0:30:37.64,0:30:42.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How's Luffy? \NThe newspapers say they don't know where he is... -OG}How's Luffy?\NThe newspaper says he's gone missing.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:30:42.62,0:30:43.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mayor...
Dialogue: 50,0:30:50.10,0:30:52.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,He escaped in a submarine.
Dialogue: 50,0:30:53.70,0:30:56.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,The Navy pursued him with everything they had,
Dialogue: 50,0:30:56.66,0:30:59.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,and they searched the area thoroughly.
Dialogue: 50,0:30:59.49,0:31:02.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But they couldn't find the ship. -OG}But the vessel eluded them.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:31:03.14,0:31:06.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{For now, at least he's alive! -OG}At least for now... he's alive!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:31:07.46,0:31:08.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 50,0:31:08.51,0:31:11.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Still, how does Vice-Admiral Garp -OG}Still, don't you think it's strange that{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:31:11.01,0:31:14.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{from Navy HQ and this bandit know each other? -OG}Navy Headquarters' Vice Admiral Garp\Nand this bandit know each other?{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:31:14.90,0:31:15.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who knows? -OG}Good point.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:31:21.33,0:31:23.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Luffy is such a fool! -OG}Luffy might be an idiot,{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:31:23.91,0:31:28.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But whatever kind of pirate he becomes,\Nit doesn't matter. I'm on his side. -OG}but no matter what kind of pirate\Nhe becomes, I will {\i1}always{\i0} stand beside him.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:31:30.70,0:31:33.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,When I think about how he must be feeling,
Dialogue: 50,0:31:33.50,0:31:35.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's like my heart is getting torn in half. -OG}it only breaks my heart.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:31:44.01,0:31:47.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Luffy{\i0}!
Dialogue: 50,0:31:47.28,0:31:53.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Don't give in to the pain! -OG}You'll get through this{\i0}!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:31:57.60,0:32:00.35,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now, we turn far away... -OG}Now, we take a look far away...{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:32:00.35,0:32:04.70,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{to the second half of the Grand Line, The New World. -OG}to somewhere in the second half\Nof the Grand Line, the New World.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:32:29.52,0:32:31.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Red Hair...
Dialogue: 50,0:32:33.12,0:32:35.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,How can I thank you for this?
Dialogue: 50,0:32:37.07,0:32:39.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't be ridiculous. -OG}Don't even mention it.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:32:39.82,0:32:43.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He might have been my enemy, but Whitebeard was a pirate worthy of respect. -OG}Though he and I were foes, Whitebeard\Ndeserved the respect he commanded.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:32:44.75,0:32:47.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Even Sengoku thought so. -OG}Even Sengoku agrees.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:32:49.21,0:32:52.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, it's time for us to go. -OG}Well, it's time we parted ways.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:32:52.48,0:32:54.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Sure... Thanks. -OG}Yeah. Thanks.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:32:55.30,0:32:59.32,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy, this must be difficult for you.
Dialogue: 50,0:33:00.21,0:33:04.07,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{I was surprised when I heard about Ace's last actions. -OG}Word of Ace's final moments\Ntook me by surprise.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:33:04.79,0:33:07.53,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Take back what you just said!{Flashback to Marineford 13 timestamp 22:03}
Dialogue: 50,0:33:07.53,0:33:11.10,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't make fun of the man who saved my life! -OG}Don't you dare mock the man who saved me!{Z- This rewrite will no longer match what's in Marineford.}{Flashback to Marineford 13 @timestamp 24:38}
Dialogue: 50,0:33:11.10,0:33:15.01,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{The name of this era is "Whitebeard"! -OG}This era belongs to Whitebeard!{Z- This rewrite will no longer match what's in Marineford.}{Flashback to Marineford 13 @timestamp 24:44}
Dialogue: 50,0:33:19.69,0:33:24.85,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{He behaved just like Captain Roger. -OG}His actions were unmistakably... Captain Roger's.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:33:27.22,0:33:32.56,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{There were times when I wanted the captain to run away... -OG}I often wished my captain would retreat.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:33:33.31,0:33:35.38,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{I even wanted him to cry. -OG}I wished he would cry.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:33:40.47,0:33:42.77,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{Listen to me, Luffy. -OG}Pay attention, Luffy.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:33:43.11,0:33:49.00,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{Knowing both victory and defeat, running away and shedding tears... -OG}When you experience both victory and defeat,\Nwhen you flee from battle and shed tears,{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:33:49.39,0:33:52.17,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{That is how men grow up. -OG}that is when you become a man.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:34:03.10,0:34:05.59,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's okay for you to cry. -OG}Allow yourself to cry.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:34:07.76,0:34:09.62,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Overcome this!
Dialogue: 50,0:34:25.38,0:34:30.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Damn it all! I'm so weak!\NI can't protect anything! -OG}Dammit! I'm so weak!\NI can't protect anyone!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:34:30.11,0:34:32.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 50,0:34:32.42,0:34:34.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 50,0:34:34.42,0:34:37.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Go away...! Just leave me alone!
Dialogue: 50,0:34:37.19,0:34:42.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I cannot do that!\NI cannot let you hurt yourself any more than you already have! -OG}I can't do that! If I did, that would mean\Nletting you hurt yourself further!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:34:44.42,0:34:47.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's my own body! I can do whatever I want with it! -OG}It's my body to hurt!\NI'll do what I want to it!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:34:47.54,0:34:51.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If so, then Ace-san's body was his own too. -OG}Then by the same token, Ace-{\i1}san{\i0}\Nwas allowed to hurt his own body...{Z- DemonRin, this line gets a bit iffy if we don't word it just right. Maybe you'll have some ideas when you get to it.}
Dialogue: 50,0:34:51.40,0:34:53.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He was free to die, regardless of what we wanted! -OG}and died regardless of how we felt!{Z- DemonRin, this line gets a bit iffy if we don't word it just right. Maybe you'll have some ideas when you get to it.}
Dialogue: 50,0:34:53.87,0:34:56.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Be quiet! -OG}Just shut up!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:34:56.14,0:34:58.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The next time you say something,\NI'll beat the crap out of you! -OG}One more word, and I'll kick your ass!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:34:58.68,0:35:01.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If that will make you feel better then go ahead and try! -OG}Then try it, if you think it'll help!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:35:02.36,0:35:07.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm quite weakened myself, but I will not lose to you.\NNot as you are now! -OG}I, too, am injured, but I won't lose.\NNot as you currently are!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:35:08.10,0:35:09.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 50,0:35:09.98,0:35:11.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Pistol!
Dialogue: 50,0:35:36.17,0:35:38.02,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Jinbe...
Dialogue: 50,0:35:38.99,0:35:41.97,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,While I was out chasing Teach...
Dialogue: 50,0:35:43.36,0:35:46.56,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,I met my little brother\Nfor the first time in three years...
Dialogue: 50,0:35:46.56,0:35:48.61,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,in the Kingdom of Arabasta.
Dialogue: 50,0:35:49.33,0:35:53.33,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,As soon as I saw him, I felt relieved.
Dialogue: 50,0:35:55.21,0:35:57.10,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why do you think that is? -OG}Do you know why?{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:36:02.73,0:36:05.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ow! That hurts!
Dialogue: 50,0:36:07.18,0:36:10.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I said that hurts, you little brat! -OG}I said that hurts, you punk!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:36:15.85,0:36:19.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Can you not see anything?! -OG}What happened to your perspective?!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:36:19.52,0:36:23.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The confidence that you'll overcome all obstacles... -OG}Where's that confidence that\Nsaw you through every obstacle?!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:36:23.06,0:36:26.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Your strength, that you've never doubted before... -OG}Or that strength you never once doubted?!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:36:26.63,0:36:32.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{A horde of enemies ruthlessly shattered your beliefs,\Nand rendered you unable to do a thing...-OG}A horde of enemies suddenly shatters your\Nbeliefs and renders you unable to do a thing...{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:36:32.11,0:36:35.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And then there's your brother,\Nwho was your guiding light... -OG}Your brother was your guiding light!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:36:35.10,0:36:37.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You have lost so many things. -OG}Indeed, this is a great loss.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:36:37.61,0:36:43.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The great obstacle known as the world\Nis blocking your vision! -OG}There's something obstructing your view\Nof the entire world around you!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:36:45.00,0:36:47.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{As you are now, you cannot see anything! -OG}You can no longer see the path ahead!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:36:47.84,0:36:50.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're being consumed by dark clouds of regret and self-blame! -OG}Dark clouds of regret and guilt consume you!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:36:51.48,0:36:54.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It might be hard for you, but Luffy! -OG}Your pain overwhelms you, Luffy,{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:36:54.34,0:36:56.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You have to defeat those feelings! -OG}but fight it!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:36:56.74,0:36:59.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't just count everything you've lost! -OG}You can't just dwell on your loss!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:37:00.12,0:37:02.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What's gone is gone!
Dialogue: 50,0:37:02.20,0:37:06.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But ask yourself this:\Nwhat remains?! -OG}But ask yourself this:\NWhat do you still have?!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:37:54.12,0:37:57.56,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Luffy, don't play around up here! -OG}Luffy, don't mess around up here!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:37:57.56,0:37:59.19,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're disrupting my training! -OG}My regimen needs focus!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:38:04.16,0:38:07.66,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy, hurry and get everyone into position!
Dialogue: 50,0:38:07.66,0:38:09.50,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{A storm is coming! -OG}A storm's just ahead!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:38:11.09,0:38:16.04,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Luffy, watch me!\NI'm about to catch a huge fish! -OG}Luffy, check it out!\NYou'll bear witness as I snag a huge fish!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:38:19.35,0:38:23.11,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Luffy, I'm almost done. Just wait patiently! -OG}Luffy, it's almost done.\NBe patient and wait!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:38:24.28,0:38:28.28,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Luffy, no matter how badly you get hurt, it'll be fine. -OG}Luffy, no matter the injury, you'll be fine!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:38:28.28,0:38:30.92,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Because I'm gonna fix you up! -OG}I'll always just fix you up, good as new!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:38:35.10,0:38:36.46,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh, Luffy.
Dialogue: 50,0:38:37.02,0:38:40.76,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you're interested in archaeology,\Ndo you want me to teach you? -OG}If you're interested,\NI can teach you about archaeology.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:38:43.59,0:38:48.52,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, Luffy! The Cola Engine\Nis running perfectly today. -OG}Hey, Luffy! The cola engine\Nis purring like a kitten today!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:38:49.58,0:38:52.54,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{You can leave the Sunny to me! -OG}Don't worry 'bout the {\i0}Sunny{\i1}!\NJust leave 'er to me!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:38:53.30,0:38:57.77,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Luffy-san, good morning!\NIt is morning! -OG}Luffy-{\i0}san{\i1}, good day to you! It's morning!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:38:57.77,0:39:00.58,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well then, I shall play a morning tune! -OG}Well then, let's get started with a morning ditty!{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:39:08.02,0:39:09.66,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 50,0:39:09.66,0:39:11.36,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 50,0:39:11.36,0:39:19.87,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 50,0:39:19.87,0:39:21.81,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy-{\i0}san{\i1}!
Dialogue: 50,0:39:22.05,0:39:23.77,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 50,0:39:35.81,0:39:37.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,My crew...
Dialogue: 50,0:39:37.98,0:39:40.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I still have my crew!
Dialogue: 50,0:39:40.38,0:39:42.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Zoro! Nami! Usopp!
Dialogue: 50,0:39:42.67,0:39:45.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sanji! Chopper! Robin!
Dialogue: 50,0:39:45.26,0:39:47.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Franky! Brook!
Dialogue: 50,0:39:47.70,0:39:49.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,My friends are still here!
Dialogue: 50,0:39:52.28,0:39:53.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 50,0:39:54.90,0:39:58.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We agreed on a meeting place... -OG}We promised to meet up somewhere.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:39:58.78,0:40:01.78,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Everyone, let's meet up by the Sunny in three days! -OG}Guys, meet back at the {\i0}Sunny{\i1} in three days!{Z}{Flashback to Sabaody}
Dialogue: 50,0:40:01.78,0:40:03.38,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 50,0:40:04.62,0:40:06.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I have to go... -OG}I gotta get there,{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:40:06.35,0:40:08.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm pretty late, though... -OG}even though I'm running late.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:40:08.98,0:40:12.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they're all waiting for me!
Dialogue: 50,0:40:13.51,0:40:18.46,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{What I saw there... Jinbe... -OG}It's because of what I saw there... Jinbe...{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:40:20.92,0:40:23.86,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Since I have a clumsy little brother, -OG}I have a reckless little brother,{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:40:24.85,0:40:26.94,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm worried about you as a big brother. -OG}which worries your big brother.{Z- Viz says "A kid brother like you makes a big brother worry."}
Dialogue: 50,0:40:27.47,0:40:30.91,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm sure he's caused you guys a lot of trouble, too. -OG}And I'm sure he does nothing\Nbut stress you all out.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:40:31.15,0:40:33.31,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Take care of him for me.
Dialogue: 50,0:40:34.38,0:40:40.58,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{I saw that he's no longer the same old Luffy\Nwho'd always chase after me. -OG}I saw that Luffy's no longer that kid\Nwho couldn't help but follow me everywhere.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:40:40.85,0:40:42.86,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's... -OG}You see now...{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:40:45.34,0:40:48.35,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{got a reliable crew of his own. -OG}he has a crew he can rely on.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:40:49.86,0:40:53.06,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{No matter what happens, he'll be alright. -OG}No matter what happens, he'll be just fine.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:40:53.61,0:40:56.10,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{I was relieved. -OG}I was so relieved.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:41:00.20,0:41:02.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I want to see them soon... -OG}I... wanna see them.{Z}
Dialogue: 50,0:41:02.89,0:41:06.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I want to see them again! -OG}I really wanna see them!{Z}
